      Non-zero values (see §ErrorCodes below):
        0x0001  HOMING_TIMEOUT     Lift did not reach limit switch within 15 s.
        0x0002  INSERTION_FAULT    Linear actuator did not complete stroke within 5 s.
        0x0004  SERVO_STALL        SG90 servo stall detected (current overload).
        0x0008  MAGAZINE_EMPTY     MagazineCount reached 0; Start inhibited.
        0x0010  COMMS_WATCHDOG     OPC UA session watchdog expired (configurable, default 120 s).
        0x0020  ACTUATOR_RETRACT   Linear actuator failed to retract within 4 s.
      Codes are OR-combined if multiple faults are present.
      Cleared by the Reset method (state ERROR -> IDLE).
